{
  "id": "nce3-l48",
  "title": "Lesson 48: The Silent Village",
  "audio": "/audio/nce3/48－The Silent Village.mp3",
  "image": "/images/coming-soon.jpg",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Lesson 48",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 0.43,
      "endTime": 2.44,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Lesson",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "课程，第...课"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "The silent village",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.45,
      "endTime": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Why was the village silent?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 10.01,
      "endTime": 14.6
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "In this much-travelled world, there are still thousands of places which are inaccessible to tourists.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 14.61,
      "endTime": 23.06,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "We always assume that villagers in remote places are friendly and hospitable.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 23.07,
      "endTime": 29.73,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "But people who are cut off not only from foreign tourists, but even from their own countrymen can be hostile to travellers.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 29.74,
      "endTime": 40.01,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Visits to really remote villages are seldom enjoyable--as my wife and I discovered during a tour through the Balkans.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 40.02,
      "endTime": 48.8,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "My",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "我的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "We had spent several days in a small town and visited a number of old churches in the vicinity.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 48.81,
      "endTime": 56.12,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Number",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "号码，数字"
          },
          {
            "word": "Old",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "老的，旧的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "These attracted many visitors, for they were not only of great architectural interest, but contained a large number of beautifully preserved frescoes as well.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 56.13,
      "endTime": 67.94,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Number",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "号码，数字"
          },
          {
            "word": "Well",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "健康的，良好的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "On the day before our departure, several bus loads of tourists descended on the town.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 67.95,
      "endTime": 74.49,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "This was more than we could bear, so we decided to spend our last day exploring the countryside.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 74.5,
      "endTime": 82.85,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Taking a path which led out of the town, we crossed a few fields until we came to a dense wood.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 82.86,
      "endTime": 90.37
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "We expected the path to end abruptly, but we found that it traced its way through the trees.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 90.38,
      "endTime": 98.21,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "We tramped through the wood for over two hours until we arrived at a deep stream.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 98.22,
      "endTime": 104.53,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "We could see that the path continued on the other side, but we had no idea how we could get across the stream.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 104.54,
      "endTime": 113.49,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "How",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "怎样，如何"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Suddenly my wife spotted a boat moored to the bank.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 113.5,
      "endTime": 117.75,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "My",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "我的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "In it there was a boatman fast asleep.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 117.76,
      "endTime": 121.37,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "We gently woke him up and asked him to ferry us to the other side.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 121.38,
      "endTime": 126.66
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Though he was reluctant to do so at first, we eventually persuaded him to take us.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 126.67,
      "endTime": 133.22,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The path led to a tiny village perched on the steep sides of a mountain.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 133.23,
      "endTime": 139.38
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The place consisted of a straggling unmade road which was lined on either side by small houses.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 139.39,
      "endTime": 146.92
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Even under a clear blue sky, the village looked forbidding, as all the houses were built of grey mud bricks.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 146.93,
      "endTime": 156.08,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Blue",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "蓝色的"
          },
          {
            "word": "Grey",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "灰色的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The village seemed deserted,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 156.09,
      "endTime": 158.48
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "the only sign of life being an ugly-looking black goat on a short length of rope tied to a tree in a field nearby.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 158.49,
      "endTime": 169.11,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Black",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "黑色的"
          },
          {
            "word": "Short",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "矮的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Sitting down on a dilapidated wooden fence near the field, we opened a couple of tins of sardines and had a picnic lunch.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 169.12,
      "endTime": 178.84
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "All at once, I noticed that my wife seemed to be filled with alarm.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 178.85,
      "endTime": 184.71,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "My",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "我的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s23",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Looking up I saw that we were surrounded by children in rags who were looking at us silently as we ate.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 184.72,
      "endTime": 193.29,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s24",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "We offered them food and spoke to them kindly, but they remained motionless.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 193.3,
      "endTime": 199.92
    },
    {
      "id": "s25",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "I concluded that they were simply shy of strangers.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 199.93,
      "endTime": 204.11,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s26",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "When we later walked down the main street of the village, we were followed by a silent procession of children.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 204.12,
      "endTime": 212.45
    },
    {
      "id": "s27",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The village which had seemed deserted, immediately came to life.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 212.46,
      "endTime": 218.23
    },
    {
      "id": "s28",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Faces appeared at windows.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 218.24,
      "endTime": 220.39,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s29",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Men in shirt sleeves stood outside their houses and glared at us.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 220.4,
      "endTime": 225.77,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Shirt",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "衬衫"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s30",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Old women in black shawls peered at us from doorways.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 225.78,
      "endTime": 230.72,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Old",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "老的，旧的"
          },
          {
            "word": "Black",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "黑色的"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s31",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The most frightening thing of all was that not a sound could be heard.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 230.73,
      "endTime": 236.63,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s32",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "There was no doubt that we were unwelcome visitors.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 236.64,
      "endTime": 241.53,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s33",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "We needed no further warning.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 241.54,
      "endTime": 244.24
    },
    {
      "id": "s34",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Turning back down the main street,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 244.25,
      "endTime": 246.59
    },
    {
      "id": "s35",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "we quickened our pace and made our way rapidly towards the stream where we hoped the boatman was waiting.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 246.6,
      "endTime": 251.6,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    }
  ]
}
